<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
.E         A
 Jonim Sen xalos qilding,
.E             A
 Xochda qoning bilan yuvding!
.E/A        E/A
 Ishonaman! Ishonaman!
.E          A
 Gʻaflatdan olib chiqding,
.E         A
 Sevging ila shifolading!
.E/A        E/A
 Ishonaman! Ishonaman!

[B1]
.  B      F#m
   Baland ovozda,
.            A          B
   Deyman: oʻlimni yengding!

[C1]
.       E       A       C#m      B
   Barhayot Rabbim! Barhayot Rabbim!
.       E       A       C#m      B
   Barhayot Rabbim! Barhayot Rabbim!

[C2]
.  D            A
   Tashvishim olding, Sen bilandirman.
.       E         F#m
   Quvonamiz baland togʻlarda,
.        A            B
   Kelgaysan shuhratingda.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<aka>Barhayot Rabbim</aka>
<title>Ishonaman</title>
<author>Reuben Morgan</author>
